{"chapter_number":88,"bismillah_pre":true,"revelation_order":68,"revelation_place":"makkah","name_arabic":"الغاشية","name_complex":"Al-Ghāshiyah","name_simple":"Al-Ghashiyah","verses_count":26,"pages":[592,592],"meaning":{"text":"The Overwhelming","en":"The Overwhelming","id":"Hari Pembalasan"},"verses":[[[1,5968,"88:1","هَلْ أَتَاكَ حَدِيثُ الْغَاشِيَةِ",["Has not there come to you the news of the overwhelming calamity?","Sudahkah sampai kepadamu berita tentang (hari Kiamat)?"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[2,5969,"88:2","وُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ خَاشِعَةٌ",["(Some) faces on that day shall be downcast,","Pada hari itu banyak wajah yang tertunduk terhina,"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[3,5970,"88:3","عَامِلَةٌ نَّاصِبَةٌ",["Laboring, toiling,","(karena) bekerja keras lagi kepayahan,"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[4,5971,"88:4","تَصْلَىٰ نَارًا حَامِيَةً",["Entering into burning fire,","mereka memasuki api yang sangat panas (neraka),"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[5,5972,"88:5","تُسْقَىٰ مِنْ عَيْنٍ آنِيَةٍ",["Made to drink from a boiling spring.","diberi minum dari sumber mata air yang sangat panas."],592,30,60,237,null,null],[6,5973,"88:6","لَّيْسَ لَهُمْ طَعَامٌ إِلَّا مِن ضَرِيعٍ",["They shall have no food but of thorns,","Tidak ada makanan bagi mereka selain dari pohon yang berduri,"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[7,5974,"88:7","لَّا يُسْمِنُ وَلَا يُغْنِي مِن جُوعٍ",["Which will neither fatten nor avail against hunger.","yang tidak menggemukkan dan tidak menghilangkan lapar."],592,30,60,237,null,null],[8,5975,"88:8","وُجُوهٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ نَّاعِمَةٌ",["(Other) faces on that day shall be happy,","Pada hari itu banyak (pula) wajah yang berseri-seri,"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[9,5976,"88:9","لِّسَعْيِهَا رَاضِيَةٌ",["Well-pleased because of their striving,","merasa senang karena usahanya (sendiri),"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[10,5977,"88:10","فِي جَنَّةٍ عَالِيَةٍ",["In a lofty garden,","(mereka) dalam surga yang tinggi,"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[11,5978,"88:11","لَّا تَسْمَعُ فِيهَا لَاغِيَةً",["Wherein you shall not hear vain talk.","di sana (kamu) tidak mendengar perkataan yang tidak berguna."],592,30,60,237,null,null],[12,5979,"88:12","فِيهَا عَيْنٌ جَارِيَةٌ",["Therein is a fountain flowing,","Di sana ada mata air yang mengalir."],592,30,60,237,null,null],[13,5980,"88:13","فِيهَا سُرُرٌ مَّرْفُوعَةٌ",["Therein are thrones raised high,","Di sana ada dipan-dipan yang ditinggikan,"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[14,5981,"88:14","وَأَكْوَابٌ مَّوْضُوعَةٌ",["And drinking-cups ready placed,","dan gelas-gelas yang tersedia (di dekatnya),"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[15,5982,"88:15","وَنَمَارِقُ مَصْفُوفَةٌ",["And cushions set in a row,","dan bantal-bantal sandaran yang tersusun,"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[16,5983,"88:16","وَزَرَابِيُّ مَبْثُوثَةٌ",["And carpets spread out.","dan permadani-permadani yang terhampar."],592,30,60,237,null,null],[17,5984,"88:17","أَفَلَا يَنظُرُونَ إِلَى الْإِبِلِ كَيْفَ خُلِقَتْ",["Will they not then consider the camels, how they are created?","Maka tidakkah mereka memperhatikan unta, bagaimana diciptakan?"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[18,5985,"88:18","وَإِلَى السَّمَاءِ كَيْفَ رُفِعَتْ",["And the heaven, how it is reared aloft,","dan langit, bagaimana ditinggikan?"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[19,5986,"88:19","وَإِلَى الْجِبَالِ كَيْفَ نُصِبَتْ",["And the mountains, how they are firmly fixed,","Dan gunung-gunung bagaimana ditegakkan?"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[20,5987,"88:20","وَإِلَى الْأَرْضِ كَيْفَ سُطِحَتْ",["And the earth, how it is made a vast expanse?","Dan bumi bagaimana dihamparkan?"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[21,5988,"88:21","فَذَكِّرْ إِنَّمَا أَنتَ مُذَكِّرٌ",["Therefore do remind, for you are only a reminder.","Maka berilah peringatan, karena sesungguhnya engkau (Muhammad) hanyalah pemberi peringatan."],592,30,60,237,null,null],[22,5989,"88:22","لَّسْتَ عَلَيْهِم بِمُصَيْطِرٍ",["You are not a watcher over them;","Engkau bukanlah orang yang berkuasa atas mereka,"],592,30,60,237,null,null],[23,5990,"88:23","إِلَّا 